title: ROM Manager.apk
description:
"ROM Manager is a great app for root users who regularly tinker with their phone's 

ROMs. The app eases the process of finding, flashing, and backing up your ROMs. With 

ROM Manager, you can Organize and perform backups and restores all from within the 

Android. It is essentially creating a recovery point for your Android and installs 

the ROMs with just one click."





This app can find, download, and install new roms for your android phone/tablet.

This application can also install Clockwork Mod Recovery.img on your device if you choose to!!!
